Description.Title: The Top Of The Jetty
Description.Body: You are at the top of an old wooden jetty. You can move west onto the jetty.

Description.Title: On the Jetty
Description.Body: You are on a rotten jetty, extending out into the dark lake. Mist surrounds you, and you can barely see the surface of the mysterious water.

Description.Title: The Tavern
Description.Body: You are in a tavern. It smells strange in here.
